item.title: CVE-2021-24541|2024-08-03T19:35:20.103Z -- unknown -- wonder%20pdf%20embed
item.description: The Wonder PDF Embed WordPress plugin before 1.7 does not escape parameters of its wonderplugin_pdf shortcode, which could allow users with a role as low as Contributor to perform Stored XSS attacks.
